import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.tanh(x1)
    v1 = jnp.subtract(v0, x1)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(x0, v1)
    v3 = jnp.multiply(v0, x0)
    v4 = jnp.add(v2, v1)
    v5 = jnp.minimum(v4, x1)
    v6 = jnp.add(v5, x1)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(x2, x0)
    return v7
